    This can be an introduction to the gEAR Search.
  </p>
  <h3>How to Search</h3>
  <p>
  	To begin a search in gEAR use the search bar on the left of the screen.
  </p>
  <div>
    <img src="img/gear_manual_img/search_start.png" alt="How to search">
  </div>
  <br />
  <p>
  	A single gene, or group of genes can be searched: 
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Single gene: "sox2"</li>
    <li>Group of genes: "fgf8 fam40b pou4f3"</li>
  </ul>
